Package: dghrank
Title: Construct Draper-Gittoes-Helkey Institution Rankings
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-12-10
Authors@R: c(person("Daniel", "Helkey", email = "dhelkey@ucsc.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
				person("David", "Draper", role = "aut",
					email = "draper@ucsc.edu"),
				person("Jessica", "Liu", role = "ctb",
					email = "jbliu@stanford.edu"),
				person("Lucy", "Greenberg", role = "ctb",
					email = "LGreenberg@vtoxford.org"),
				person("Daniel", "Kirsner", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides functions for ranking institution quality as measured by to binary performance indicators, accounting for categorical and continious risk adjusters. Rankings computed according using Draper-Gittoes-Helkey (2018) methodology. Functions are provided to run analysis on individual performance indicators and generate composite scores.  Main fitting functions (fitBabyMonitor() and scoreComposite()) intended for CPQCC/VON usage, but sub-functions provided for probit and Bayesian linear regression implemented with sparse matrices.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
